@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Home/Index.css" asp-append-version="true" />

<div id="banner" class="container-fluid">
    <div class="swiper mySwiper">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            <div class="swiper-slide">
                <img src="~/images/banner/Home/banner.jpg" alt="" />
                <h3>Derek獨立式浴缸新上市 打造身心專屬舒壓時光</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-slide">
                <img src="~/images/banner/Home/banner02.jpg" alt="" />
                <h3>「淨未來」微電腦馬桶座系列享受瞬熱式潔淨 冬季溫暖就靠它</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
        <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="Most_Popular">
    <div class="title">今日最熱門</div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="frame">
            <div class="image"><img src="~/images/hotad1.jpg" alt="" /></div>
            <p class="describe">
                母親節來臨，以全新獨立式浴缸系列與「淨未來瞬熱式微電腦馬桶座」,給天下媽媽們一份療癒身心之禮
            </p>
            <div class="keywords">
                <ul>
                    <li>#淨未來</li>
                    <li>#全自動</li>
                    <li>#冷熱SPA按摩</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="frame">
            <div class="image"><img src="~/images/hotad2.jpg" alt="" /></div>
            <p class="describe">
                Derek獨立式美型缸系列，以壓克力材質形塑柔和輪廓，分為經典款、魅力款、個性款、古典款，造型多樣、擺放自由度高，完美匹配多種裝潢風格。
            </p>
            <div class="keywords">
                <ul>
                    <li>#浴缸</li>
                    <li>#新品</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
    <p>Learn about <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/core">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a>.</p>
</div>
